Description: Fender Standard Stratocaster MIM 1993 This is an outstanding Stratocaster! I sent a request to Fender asking them for the year of manufacture and original specifications. I was surprised to learn that it was made in 1993. It has a few scratches here and there and normal signs of wear, but it is in crazy good shape for a guitar that is 25 years old! It sounds and plays great! The frets have minor wear with lots of life left. It has a minor finish crack on one side of the neck pocket. This is very common on MIMs. This guitar comes with a nice hard case and tremolo arm. It has freshly polished frets and a new set of DAddario 9s. I will copy below what Fender sent to me regarding this guitar. Don’t let this one get away! Shipping to lower 48 states only. *MN3127705/ 0134602(706)/ FENDER STD STRAT MN BLK W/C/ 11-26-1993.
